 49	- `title`
 50	- `description`
 51	- `audioUrl` (local path URI hoặc remote URL)
 52	- `coverArtUrl` (nullable)
 53	- `genre`
 54	- `durationMs` (nullable; có thể lấy sau khi load MediaMetadataRetriever)
 55	- `isPublic` (bool)
 56	- `createdAt`
